tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE Interview_Transcripts (
  transcript_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  interviewer_name TEXT,
  interviewee_name TEXT,
  transcript_text TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE InterviewTranscripts (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  transcript TEXT,
  interviewer_name TEXT,
  interviewee_name TEXT,
  interview_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE FieldNotes (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  note TEXT,
  researcher_name TEXT,
  field_location TEXT,
  note_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE Researchers (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  researcher_name TEXT,
  research_focus TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE ResearchProjects (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  project_name TEXT,
  start_date DATE,
  end_date DATE
)
